<br />

<br />
Navigate to your Everquest folder.  Right click on the files to open their properties, and check the box for READ ONLY.  This will prevent the machine from actually writing to those files.
<br />

<br />
I'm not sure if this will solve your problem.  Certainly do the other stuff people have recommended as well.</span></td>
