				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Forced to stop AE kiting<a name="24971"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 2 04 12:47 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I had this same problem and tried EVERYTHING to fix it.  I finally figured out that I had to stop the Mcafee Virusscan service to stop the pauses from happening.  Simply disabling it using the icon  in the taskbar area won't stop the pausing.  You have to go into Control Panel-&gt;Adminitstrative Tools-&gt;Services and explicitly stop the Mcafee Virusscan service (I forgot the actual name).  When you reboot, the service will start again or you can go back and explicitly start it after you exit EQ. </span></td>
